===Noun===
'''suspender''' (''Plural:'' '''suspenders''')

#Something or someone who suspends.
#{{US}} An item of apparel consisting of a strap worn over the shoulder and used hold up trousers. Called [[braces]] in other parts of the world.
#{{UK}} An item of apparel consiting of a band of elastic material, worn around the thigh and used to hold up a [[stocking]]; a [[garter]]


